  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provision of Humanitarian Coordination and Shelter and Settlements Assistance for Crisis-Affected Populations in Ethiopia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The combined impacts of desert locusts, the effects of the COVID-19 pandemic, and ongoing flare-ups due to inter-communal tension have fueled existing conflicts and enabled new ones to emerge in Ethiopia. Immediate life-saving priorities of crisis-affected populations in Ethiopia include critical Shelter and Settlement and Humanitarian Coordination and Information Management interventions. Through this project, IOM is contributing to the improvement of living conditions and the well-being of crisis-affected populations in Ethiopia through Humanitarian Coordination and Information Management, and Shelter and Settlements interventions.</narrative>
  </description>
